
<div class="ic-flash-warning" style="width: auto !important;">
  <div class="ic-flash__icon" aria-hidden="true">
    <i class="icon-warning"></i>
  </div>
  Warning: <span class="bold">This action cannot be undone</span>.  Students placed far ahead in a course cannot be moved in previous sequenced lesson activities.
</div>

<br/>

<div class="ic-flash-info" style="width: auto !important;">
  <div class="ic-flash__icon" aria-hidden="true">
    <i class="icon-info"></i>
  </div>
  Info: It can take a few minutes to custom place a student.  Click <span class="bold">Update</span class="bold"> to continue working in the system while this action is performed.
</div>

<p>Please select an initial place to start this student at.</p>

<div class="ic-Form-control">
  <label class="ic-Label" for="content_tag_id">Unit to start</label>
  <select class="ic-Input" name="content_tag_id" id="content_tag_id" class="">
    {{#each context_modules}}
      <optgroup label="{{name}}">
        {{#each this.content_tags}}
          <option value="{{this.id}}">{{this.title}}</option>
        {{/each}}
      </optgroup>
    {{/each}}
  </select>
</div>